{"tid":2108074,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"部份樹蛙的肚腩是藍色的緣故","createTime":"2020-07-14T09:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T17:10:20.000Z","uid":38861,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1125e36deb89f7b3ef447b9e479f433279a32177","tid":2108074,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:52:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oDMHSdy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoDMHSdy.jpg&h=d0375dd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當我們唔小心撞傷的時候，某部份紅血球會破爛，釋放出名為膽綠素（Biliverdin)的物質。<br />\n<br />\n基於膽綠素對人體有害，我哋身體好快就會將它分解及排出體外。而傷口瘀傷嗰種紫綠色，就係由膽綠素所做成的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有趣的是，有科學家發現，某系列品種樹蛙的體內一直存在比人體高達四部有多的膽綠素濃度，但完全無壞無痛，生活一切正常。<br />\n<br />\n最後他們發現，那些樹蛙體內一隻名為Serpine的蛋白質會與膽綠素結合在一起，其作用究竟是如何暫時仲未了解得到。<br />\n<br />\n但基於膽綠素呈紫藍色的關係，那些樹蛙肚腩會呈現清晰的藍色，而由如牠們肚腩以外的皮膚是黃色緣故，黃加藍輾轉就變成為綠色。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource:<a href=\"https://www.pnas.org/content/early/2020/07/09/2006771117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pnas.org%2Fcontent%2Fearly%2F2020%2F07%2F09%2F2006771117&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuHwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=3a4bc9c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pnas.org/content/early/2020/07/09/2006771117</a>"},{"pid":"ad1f0f6fcc89edec1e489dbd95c8839f6c8637da","tid":2108074,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea39f27891aca2b318c6d8e0aef65c10d69b97e","tid":2108074,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:54:41.000Z","msg":"學野"},{"pid":"891a8744e57416dd562746b88c98c50cec4d81e8","tid":2108074,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:54:44.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"336f5c92778a6a83884c66f96715356f26db9829","tid":2108074,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:56:30.000Z","msg":"為左適應吹脹自己呱呱叫嘅天賦被動技能"},{"pid":"c07851def3de7d93ea6b6d31e2ec1a33611b00a8","tid":2108074,"uid":33609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:57:41.000Z","msg":"薯仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0344a5759892bd6a435181b443c1f143a259855","tid":2108074,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b18f693f9fb8b2f61f4ff47859e6c37d56fa6f24","tid":2108074,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:05:03.000Z","msg":"好想吉爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ea3d8b4e2e4f6b8d360707a5f73949f82ebeac","tid":2108074,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:35:11.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"65e465374ee5b06c452503aea766b16e699b7cb2","tid":2108074,"uid":155238,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T11:22:35.000Z","msg":"藍血人係真㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9058c8a672f89a4107439deade7d05ca4011b7e","tid":2108074,"uid":185985,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T11:59:47.000Z","msg":"冷門知識專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d560155b1dbb9e585ab738c95f46bce6da7d3f","tid":2108074,"uid":202256,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:38:23.000Z","msg":"樹蛙好藍 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ea5ba631b3dde2184ed1188e2db2ad419655e5","tid":2108074,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:58:15.000Z","msg"